# AI Checklist and Verification Workflow

- Convert uploaded SOW/brief documents into structured deliverable checklists with deterministic JSON output.
- Keep prompts and parsers focused on extractable deliverables and required technical credentials.
- Require human approval ("Ready for Client") before publishing AI-generated checklist changes.
- Track deliverable lifecycle as explicit states (pending, verified, client-confirmed).
- Verification logic should compare required format against uploaded asset evidence before marking verified.
- Preserve an auditable history of key handoff events (uploaded, verified, published, downloaded, signed off).
